   - **Grammatik in BNF (Backus-Naur-Form)**:
     ```
     <Lumini> ::= "Lumini(" <Entity> "," <Property>* ")"
     <Entity> ::= <ID> | <Type>
     <Property> ::= <Key> "=" <Value>
     <Value> ::= <Number> | <String> | <Lumini>
     ```
